org.odata4j.edm
Class EdmType

java.lang.Object
  org.odata4j.edm.EdmType

public class EdmType
extends Object

A type in the EDM type system. Simple types are exposed as constants and associated with one or more java-types.

See Also:
[msdn] Simple Types (EDM)
